                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48238107/">见素抱朴</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">整本书都是解说周易的系辞，文笔都是用白话，不会有人看不懂。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

