            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27890727">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">卑者近也。不是自卑！</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-01 22:51</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                卑者近也。不是自卑！
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

