      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="27890813">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65569191/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u65569191-2.jpg" alt="无男" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27890813/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27890813/" class="">第13页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65569191/" class=" " title="无男">无男</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27890813">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">古人在婚书上写着“上昭天地神明祖先，两人永结同心”的字样，不像现在的结婚证书是为了将来离婚、打官司时用的。还要有介绍人，准备将来上厅当证人！这是西方的风俗。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-01 22:57</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                古人在婚书上写着“上昭天地神明祖先，两人永结同心”的字样，不像现在的结婚证书是为了将来离婚、打官司时用的。还要有介绍人，准备将来上厅当证人！这是西方的风俗。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27890813/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
